grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">Ζε̄νὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐριγδούπ̣οιο κ̣όρε̄ι γλαυκο̄́πῑ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἀ͡θ\u003C/span>ε̄́νε̄ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">Θρίπυλος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> εὐξάμεν̣ος τε̄́νδ’ ἀνέθε̄κε̣ θεᾶι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">ΖΕ̄ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΡΙΓΔΟΥ.ΟΙΟ.ΟΡΕ̄ΙΓΛΑΥΚΟ̄ΠῙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Α͡Θ\u003C/span>Ε̄ΝΕ̄Ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">ΘΡΙΠΥΛΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΥΞΑΜΕ.ΟΣΤΕ̄ΝΔΑΝΕΘΕ̄Κ.ΘΕΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Arena (IGASM 3)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>To the bright-eyed Athena daughter of loud-thundering Zeus, Thripylos invoking dedicated this (kylix?) to the goddess.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Per Atena dagli occhi lucenti figlia di Zeus altitonante, Thripylos invocante ha dedicato questa (kylix?) alla dea.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Inscription incised in neat characters before firing on a base of a medium-sized vase. The inscription is a couplet of poetic inspiration whose first hemistich is the same as the beginning of v. 3 of the Homeric Hymn to Hera (Ζε̄νὸς ἐριγδούποιο). It is followed by another Homeric formula (γλαυκο̄́πῑ Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι) with a shortened form γλαυκο̄́πῑ rather than the recurring γλαυκῶπιν. The form κόρε̄ι has a vocalism that is attested in Euboea (cf. \u003Ca href=\"https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000747552\" target=\"_blank\">Bechtel 1921-1924\u003C/a>, 74). τε̄́νδ(ε) could refer to κύλικα but could also indicate something else. It is interesting to note that a clay and headless figurine of Athena was found near the vase (Manni Piraino 1974, p. 266).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1974 266, pl. XLII.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hansen 1983 392 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">8\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1994 45, pl. XIV.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1  5-15  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[233,236,239,242,245,247,250,253,256],{"id":234,"html":235},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">Ζε̄νὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐριγδούπ̣οιο κ̣όρε̄ι γλαυκο̄́πῑ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἀ͡θ\u003C/span>ε̄́νε̄ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">Θρίπυλος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> εὐξάμεν̣ος τε̄́νδ’ ἀνέθε̄κε̣ θεᾶι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">ΖΕ̄ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΡΙΓΔΟΥ.ΟΙΟ.ΟΡΕ̄ΙΓΛΑΥΚΟ̄ΠῙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Α͡Θ\u003C/span>Ε̄ΝΕ̄Ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">ΘΡΙΠΥΛΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΥΞΑΜΕ.ΟΣΤΕ̄ΝΔΑΝΕΘΕ̄Κ.ΘΕΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":237,"html":238},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020587.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020587-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":240,"html":241},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Arena (IGASM 3)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":243,"html":244},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>To the bright-eyed Athena daughter of loud-thundering Zeus, Thripylos invoking dedicated this (kylix?) to the goddess.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":243,"html":246},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Per Atena dagli occhi lucenti figlia di Zeus altitonante, Thripylos invocante ha dedicato questa (kylix?) alla dea.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":248,"html":249},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Inscription incised in neat characters before firing on a base of a medium-sized vase. The inscription is a couplet of poetic inspiration whose first hemistich is the same as the beginning of v. 3 of the Homeric Hymn to Hera (Ζε̄νὸς ἐριγδούποιο). It is followed by another Homeric formula (γλαυκο̄́πῑ Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι) with a shortened form γλαυκο̄́πῑ rather than the recurring γλαυκῶπιν. The form κόρε̄ι has a vocalism that is attested in Euboea (cf. \u003Ca href=\"https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000747552\" target=\"_blank\">Bechtel 1921-1924\u003C/a>, 74). τε̄́νδ(ε) could refer to κύλικα but could also indicate something else. It is interesting to note that a clay and headless figurine of Athena was found near the vase (Manni Piraino 1974, p. 266).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":251,"html":252},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1974 266, pl. XLII.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001469\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hansen 1983 392 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002468\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">8\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1994 45, pl. XIV.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":254,"html":255},"handnote","  Line 1  5-15  ",{"id":257,"html":258},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[260,262,265,266],{"html":261},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa",{"id":263,"lang":123,"html":264},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">Ζε̄νὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐριγδούπ̣οιο κ̣όρε̄ι γλαυκο̄́πῑ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἀ͡θ\u003C/span>ε̄́νε̄ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">Θρίπυλος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> εὐξάμεν̣ος τε̄́νδ’ ἀνέθε̄κε̣ θεᾶι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>",{"html":261},{"id":267,"lang":123,"html":268},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζε̄νὸς\">ΖΕ̄ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΡΙΓΔΟΥ.ΟΙΟ.ΟΡΕ̄ΙΓΛΑΥΚΟ̄ΠῙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀθε̄́νε̄ι\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Α͡Θ\u003C/span>Ε̄ΝΕ̄Ι\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θρίπυλος\">ΘΡΙΠΥΛΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΥΞΑΜΕ.ΟΣΤΕ̄ΝΔΑΝΕΘΕ̄Κ.ΘΕΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.2 subscript\u003C/p>",[270,272],{"image":97,"thumb":271,"title":100},"ISic020587_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":273,"thumb":274,"title":100},"ISic020587.jpg","ISic020587-thumb.jpg",[],"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/stru